      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Generated transactions include all transactions that are automatically calculated and posted by the system to the GL based on pre-established calculation rules, or amounts based on a pre-determined schedule.  These would include recurring transactions, amortization of prepaids, interest accruals, amortization of long-term debt, etc.  Some allocations may take place at this point in the process (ie. Freight/shipping costs to business units).  This does not include transfers from sub-ledgers."/>
